=== 会徽 ===
[[佐野研二郎|佐野研二郎]]所設計的東京奧運及帕運2個會徽是從104件應徵作品當中雀屏中選，於2015年7月24日公布<ref>{{cite news | title = 抄襲爭議 東京奧運帕運會徽停用 | publisher = 中央社 | url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201509010314-1.aspx | date = 2015-09-01 | author = 楊明珠 | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2015-09-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150902190329/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201509010314-1.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。起先是被指與2年前比利時設計師奧利維·德比（Olivier Debie）為[[比利時|比利時]]的[[列日劇院|列日劇院]]所設計的商標雷同，德比要求停用會徽。[[第32屆奧林匹克運動會組織委員會|東京奧運籌委會]]於2015年9月1日正式做出決議，將停止使用佐野所設計的東京奧運及帕運的會徽<ref>{{cite news | title = 東京奧運抄襲被撤 原設計師：贏了 | publisher = 中央社 | url = https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/2797501 | date = 2015-09-01 | author = 江今葉 | accessdate = 2021-08-25 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2021-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210825063656/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/2797501 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2016年4月，以「組市松紋」圖案作為奧運及帕運的正式會徽。它採用[[江戶時代|江戶時代]]流行的「市松模樣」方格圖紋，由[[野老朝雄|野老朝雄]]所設計。<ref name="guardian-plagelogo">{{cite news|title=Tokyo Olympic Games logo embroiled in plagiarism row|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2015/jul/30/tokyo-olympics-logo-plagiarism-row|access-date=1 August 2015|work=The Guardian|date=30 July 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803111947/http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2015/jul/30/tokyo-olympics-logo-plagiarism-row|archive-date=3 August 2015|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|title=Tokyo Olympics emblem said to look similar to Belgian theater logo|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/07/30/national/tokyo-olympics-emblem-said-look-similar-belgian-theater-logo/|publisher=[[The_Japan_Times|The Japan Times]]|date=30 July 2015|access-date=30 July 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731054232/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/07/30/national/tokyo-olympics-emblem-said-look-similar-belgian-theater-logo/|archive-date=31 July 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>
